videos.description: Kansas passes the ball around the perimeter, eventually finding Lagerald Vick in the left corner for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Kansas swings it to Vick who drills a 3-pointer

videos.description: A leaping Josh Jackson catches a pass from Devonte' Graham then slams it in.
videos.headline: Jackson flies in for the catch and slam for Kansas

videos.description: Kansas' Frank Mason III takes over, drilling triples on back-to-back possessions for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Mason buries 3-pointers on back-to-back possessions for Kansas

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham strips the ball away from Oklahoma then scores on an easy lay-in on the other end.
videos.headline: Graham swipes the ball away then lays it in for Kansas

videos.description: Kansas head coach Bill Self on his team's emotions in the 1st half on senior night.
videos.headline: Self: "We just need to take a deep breath"

videos.description: Off a missed shot, Oklahoma's Rashard Odomes kicks it out to Darrion Strong-Moore who connects on a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Strong-Moore connects on a huge 3-pointer for the Sooners

videos.description: Kansas' Carlton Bragg Jr. catches a pass, then up court tries to slam it in, but has his attempt blocked by the rim.
videos.headline: Bragg Jr. has dunk attempt obliterated by the rim

videos.description: Off an inbounds pass from Frank Mason III, Josh Jackson skies to catch a lob and dunks it in.
videos.headline: Jackson dunks in alley-oop from Mason III

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham hits two 3-pointers from the right corner on back-to-back possessions.
videos.headline: Graham buries 3-pointer on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Kansas' senior guard Frank Mason III talks about what he's going to miss the most about his years at Kansas.
videos.headline: Frank Mason III on his emotions during senior night
